<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The HTTP client currently has a getLastRequest() method but no getLastResponse() method.  Adding this will make it easier to debug other Zend components that use the HTTP client internally, such as Zend_Feed or Zend_XmlRpc_Client.</p>

